<div>
  <h2>Hi!</h2>
  <p>
    On occasion, my brain cells align long enough to form what some might call
    "a thought". And sometimes, these momentary neural eclipses last long
    enough for me to capture them in digital form. So welcome to my brain's
    galaxy! Much like the Milky Way, it's mostly vacuous.
  </p>

  <h2>Projects</h2>
  {%- for project in collections.project -%}
    <div>
      <div class="post-title-group">
        <h3>
          <a href="{{ project.url }}">{{ project.data.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        <span class="post-date">{% date project.date %}</span>
      </div>
      <img class="banner-small" src="{{ project.data.banner }}"/>
      <p>{{ project.data.summary }}</p>
    </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
